  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is evaluating the efficacy of acalabrutinib in combination with bendamustine and
      rituximab (BR) compared with placebo plus BR in subjects with previously untreated mantle
      cell lymphoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
